@startuml
actor Admin
participant Frontend
participant Server
participant Database

Admin -> Frontend: Open update employee form
Frontend -> Server: GET /api/employees/:id
Server -> Database: Find employee by id
Database --> Server: Return employee data
Server --> Frontend: Return employee data
Frontend -> Admin: Display employee data in form

Admin -> Frontend: Modify employee data and submit
Frontend -> Server: PUT /api/employees/:id with updated data
Server -> Database: Update employee record
Database --> Server: Return updated employee
Server --> Frontend: Return updated employee
Frontend -> Admin: Show success or error message
@enduml
